parameters.query:
-- Find matching prospect by email
SELECT 
  id as prospect_id,
  name,
  business_name,
  prospect_type,
  lead_score,
  email
FROM prospects 
WHERE email = '{{ $json.attendee_email }}'
  AND is_active = TRUE 
  AND deleted_at IS NULL
LIMIT 1;
